{"tid":2254394,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"叱咤閉門舉行頒獎禮 港台取消頒發十優歌手","createTime":"2020-10-22T19:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T04:32:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1c7592b798925869882286310d420f089d5bdf","tid":2254394,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T19:59:10.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎最近雖然有緩和迹象，但今年受疫情影響，樂壇仿似一潭死水，冇乜好歌hit爆，本年度的樂壇頒獎禮都遭波及。據《蘋果》收到消息，明年1月1日舉行的商台「叱咤樂壇頒獎禮」將會閉門舉行，不設觀眾，但商台會book場照搞頒獎禮，歌手照上台唱歌，叱咤以Online形式直播；而港台「第43屆十大中文金曲頒獎音樂會」則沒有實體頒獎禮，只會請得獎歌手錄影節目，並安排於明年1月16日在港台電視31播出，消息指港台今年取消頒發十優歌手、最優秀流行歌手大獎及進步獎；至於新城勁爆頒獎禮，據聞同樣沒有實體頒獎禮。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201022/JKGLK2YGSFH2BBCBWPZDVK675A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201022%2FJKGLK2YGSFH2BBCBWPZDVK675A%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=dc05e316\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201022%2FJKGLK2YGSFH2BBCBWPZDVK675A%2F&h=a1060f13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201022/JKGLK2YGSFH2BBCBWPZDVK675A/</a>"},{"pid":"940df5da0c212019fd0cd470e0763405f3169910","tid":2254394,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:32:46.000Z","msg":"推"}]}